## Runtime.ReadOnlyResourceTreeBranch class

Implementation of a read-only resource tree branch node that contains child nodes. Branch nodes organize other nodes in a hierarchical structure and may optionally contain a resource value.

**Signature:**

```typescript
export declare class ReadOnlyResourceTreeBranch<T> implements IReadOnlyResourceTreeBranch<T> 
```
**Implements:** [IReadOnlyResourceTreeBranch](./ts-res.runtime.ireadonlyresourcetreebranch.md)<!-- -->&lt;T&gt;
